":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T19:58:18.000Z","msg":"放鬆啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"854b76a679d14b21e02fa1161823dff89da23fc0","tid":324894,"uid":117150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T19:58:33.000Z","msg":"可能我睇得個結果太重<br />\n比左太多不必要嘅壓力自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8617d3a08125c16bfde966bbc7b3bed8db6961fa","tid":324894,"uid":29405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T20:00:26.000Z","msg":"考試前一日打j<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"319da9261a9d710413a1d97556fe6c911a93a1a3","tid":324894,"uid":117150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T20:01:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>考試前一日打j<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n無J<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  不過聽人講打完J係咪會好訓啲？"},{"pid":"ea06effb83c990c6cd05bd0e6e8234296ed0b7ed","tid":324894,"uid":34259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T20:02:09.000Z","msg":"我明，聽下啲放鬆既純音樂，燒下香薰？"},{"pid":"db082ff6f4f7f55f01161915f63e8fe40bf3248c","tid":324894,"uid":107221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T20:03:43.000Z","msg":"失眠冇耐條女有第二個 日日係屋企瞓 瞓左第4日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e74790c5c3a7e9b83f7d47ea694df79f3d7abd8d","tid":324894,"uid":34259,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T20:04:36.000Z","msg":"我自己訓唔著既話會照合眼，<br />\n想像一個空間，中間有舊石頭不斷向下沉，我同自己講沉到底既時候就會入睡"},{"pid":"08cca3e6549bd7c7fe580d7f24e5c4ed8dc008fd","tid":324894,"uid":34259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T20:05:52.000Z","msg":"不過前提要摒除曬所有雜念<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9448bb381a1c6ff32aa552c8a8435616aa47079","tid":324894,"uid":89182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"s