傷喉嚨？如果太&quot;哽&quot; ？"},{"pid":"5ef34ab1c3384fe113bdc36c98faf8667969b8c4","tid":324894,"uid":41205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T20:18:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>訓唔著<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都係 太驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不停亂諗野</blockquote><br />\n我都係因為考試訓唔著<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我仲有半個月先考，但最近開始晚晚訓唔著<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12a47d081797b59572d993fbfc87bc8a447ae611","tid":324894,"uid":117150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T20:19:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>仲有個重點 手機擺遠d/擺出廳 如果部手機係你身邊既話好易就會拎起部手機周圍篤 唔會訓得著</blockquote><br />\n我都覺得係 坦白說我自己都真係好沈迷網路 有時都係到諗依家科技愈黎愈發達 對我黎講好事定壞事 細個無智能手機 好多時簡簡單單都開心 有手機睇既資訊多左 人知野多左 反而無咁開心 手機同時都令我耽誤或者錯過咗好多野 身邊都有人話過我太大網癮</blockquote><br />\n呢個問題我成日都係到諗 其實我已經有決心去改善佢 我前幾日特登去買左部摺機 諗住以後轉用摺機 唔再比自己用智能手機 但又落唔到手 唉 係咪比我嚇親 無諗到會就手機黎借題發揮 其實想打出黎好耐！！ 見到更加有感而發"},{"pid":"39720804f3515e191167a10bf0bbbfada3e24832","tid":324894,"uid":89182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T20:20:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>飲下酒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n又苦又傷身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔鐘意飲酒 你都少飲啲啦<br />\n我之前有個同學飲到入醫院 胃入血 到依家個胃都唔好</blockquote><br />\n呢兩日先飲晒成枝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我一係唔飲，一飲飲好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你真係要小心身體喎咁樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  你飲啲大酒定咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n甩緊架啦，指日可待<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nWhiskey rum vodka果類<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實你又唔洗飲到宿痛果隻，少少wing夠訓就得</blockquote><br />\n飲酒會唔會傷喉嚨？如果太&quot;哽&quot; ？</blockquote><br />\n唔會呀，除非你飲果d重口味，外國有賣100% alcohol 聽到都唔敢試，40度係我上限<br />\n<br />\n高梁都難入口"},{"pid":"31d923e365379ac7cfd9a1bc72d8a1942efd2652","tid":324894,"uid":117150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T20:20:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>訓唔著<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都係 太驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不停亂諗野</blockquote><br />\n我都係因為考試訓唔著<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我仲有半個月先考，但最近開始晚晚訓唔著<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實我都係諗緊應該要放鬆啲就無野 但真係好驚呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 可能係我個人由細到大都睇到成績好重"},{"pid":"1a24577f0ebb50f966296e4f2a5e21aa431a94aa","tid":324894,"uid":41205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T20:22:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>訓唔著<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都係 太驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class